{
  "stem": "1502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "It was a German headquarters the day before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "But if you want to stay just overnight, she would let us in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And we went into that house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "It was a beautiful house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "It was-- probably belonged to a very wealthy person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And we did find the German newspapers and envelopes addressed to the German headquarters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "So apparently, it was some kind of a headquarter, division headquarter, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And we stayed there overnight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Again, and there was-- there was no water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "We-- but we had plenty of cologne water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "So we washed with-- with cologne water, with toilet water, French, the best brands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And we didn't have-- there was no water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "We didn't have water to drink, it was-- but there were cases-- in the cellar, there were cases of wine and cognac.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "So that's the only thing we had to drink, even if it was not kosher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "But that's the only thing we had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "Then, we continued to walk back to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "As we walked back to Brussels, my first encounter with the-- with the German Nazis, with German anti-Semitism, was I-- we were-- as I said, we were a whole group.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And on the push cart, we had our belongings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We also had on the push cart some merchandise that we took along from Belgium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were stopped on the road by a German Feldgendarme-- that was like military police-- on a motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first thing he asked me-- it happens that we pushed that push cart in turns, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every time, two-- two men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the rest of the family were walking, like a few hundred feet away from the push cart.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
